    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.poster.avif?t=1742916808\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.webm?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.mp4?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>名人快打</strong>中，每个角色都是著名且独特的，并且有其优点和缺点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好与这个世界上有史以来最著名、最富有、最奢侈的人战斗。 从 Nicki Minaj 到 Cardi B，从 Kanye West 到 Jay-Z，探索他们的风格和获胜秘诀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每周添加新角色！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/894398b7e10f210ab51caf6e492ebf25.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/894398b7e10f210ab51caf6e492ebf25.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=368 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有自己的风格：剑、魔法、近战、空手道……选择权在你，还有更多等待你去发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/b2df6e920e43dfe3854095306c723b86.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/b2df6e920e43dfe3854095306c723b86.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=364 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以离线或在线玩：使用两个控制器在计算机上与朋友一起玩，或者与完全随机的陌生人在线玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/6ef7f5537401abab6b43adbf4afaa4de.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/6ef7f5537401abab6b43adbf4afaa4de.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备好与名人进行终极战斗！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/bca07809166594585d2b16558eb1c4c5.poster.avif?t=1742916808\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/bca07809166594585d2b16558eb1c4c5.webm?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/bca07809166594585d2b16558eb1c4c5.mp4?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
